---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Story">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-slate-950 border-b border-slate-900">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_-10%,rgba(197,168,128,0.05),rgba(255,255,255,0))]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative text-center">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500 block mb-3">Legacy & Values</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif-legal font-bold text-white tracking-wide">
        Our Story
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto text-slate-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
        Decades of institutional memory, carried forward by a new generation of legal professionals.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Narrative Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-950 font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        
        <!-- Legacy column -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="h-px w-8 bg-amber-500/50"></span>
            <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-amber-550">The Inheritance of Excellence</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-305 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Our story did not begin today. It began decades ago at <strong>3 Parliament Street, New Delhi</strong>, within the walls of one of India’s pioneer law firms — <strong>J. B. Dadachanji & Company</strong>. This was a firm that did not merely practise law; it helped shape it, offering a uniquely holistic approach to clients navigating a newly-independent, dynamic India.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-350 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Led by the legendary <strong>Mr. J. B. Dadachanji, Mr. Ravinder Narain, and Mr. O. C. Mathur</strong>, the firm became a benchmark for excellence in the Indian legal profession. That legacy of benchmark-setting is our inheritance.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-350 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            After the demise of his partners, Mr. Ravinder Narain carried the torch forward, continuing the practice in his personal capacity under the name and style of <strong>“Ravinder Narain & Company.”</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-350 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Today, the mantle has been passed to his senior associates, who founded <strong>DNA Legal</strong> to carry this profound legacy into a new era. DNA Legal is the modern manifestation of a timeless commitment to legal excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Philosophy Column -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-6 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="absolute -right-16 -bottom-16 w-36 h-36 rounded-full bg-amber-500/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <h3 class="font-serif-legal text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
            Our Philosophy
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-350 leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Client Interests First</strong>: Our client’s interests are our own. We deliver clarity in complexity, transforming intricate legal challenges into strategic advantages.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-350 leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Responsive & Commercial</strong>: Our client-focused approach is marked by an unwavering responsiveness and the commercial sensibility of a trusted in-house team.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-350 leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Different by Design</strong>: We pair deep-rooted heritage with a future-focused, technology-driven practice. We believe in quality over quantity, ensuring every client receives partner-led attention.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values & Why Us -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-950 font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500 block mb-3">Our Core Pillars</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif-legal font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Why DNA Legal</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-950 border border-slate-850 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-amber-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">01 / DECADES OF WISDOM</div>
            <h3 class="font-serif-legal text-xl font-bold text-slate-200 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Heritage that translates into instinct</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">
              Decades of institutional memory carried forward from one of India’s pioneer law firms inform the way we read a brief, anticipate the other side, and structure a strategy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-950 border border-slate-850 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-amber-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">02 / PAN-INDIA DISPUTES</div>
            <h3 class="font-serif-legal text-xl font-bold text-slate-200 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Pan-India reach, single point of accountability</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">
              Wherever the dispute is, the firm appears — with a single partner answerable for the brief from filing to satisfaction, ensuring uniform standards of advocacy and client reporting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-950 border border-slate-850 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-amber-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">03 / BUSINESS FIRST</div>
            <h3 class="font-serif-legal text-xl font-bold text-slate-200 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Commercial sensibility, by design</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">
              We tell clients when not to litigate, just as readily as we tell them when to. We measure success not by paper victories, but by the commercial results in the client's account.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
